'''氧4'''分子（O<sub>4</sub>），也被称作'''四聚氧'''。1924年，[[吉尔伯特·牛顿·路易斯|吉尔伯特·牛顿·路易斯]]首先预测了它的存在，以解释[[液氧|液氧]]不符合[[居里定律|居里定律]]（[[顺磁性|顺磁性]]物质的[[磁化率|磁化率]]与[[热力学温度|热力学温度]]成反比）的原因。<ref>{{cite journal
 | last = Lewis
 | first = Gilbert N.
 | title = The Magnetism of Oxygen and the Molecule O<sub>2</sub>
 | journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society
 | volume = 46
 | issue = 9
 | pages = 2027–2032
 | doi = 10.1021/ja01674a008
 |date=September 1924}}</ref>现在看来路易斯的预测并不准确，但不是完全错误：计算机模拟表明，虽然[[液氧|液氧]]中没有稳定的O<sub>4</sub>分子，O<sub>2</sub>分子确实倾向于形成反平行[[自旋|自旋]]的双聚体O<sub>4</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal
 | last = Oda
 | first = Tatsuki
 | coauthors = Alfredo Pasquarello
 | title = Noncollinear magnetism in liquid oxygen: A first-principles molecular dynamics study
 | journal = Physical Review B
 | volume = 70
 | issue = 134402
 | pages = 1–19
 | doi = 10.1103/PhysRevB.70.134402
 | url = http://link.aps.org/abstract/PRB/v70/e134402
 | format = abstract
 |date=October 2004}}</ref>1999年，科学家认为固态氧的ε相（压强大于10GPa下存在）中氧的存在形式为O<sub>4</sub>。<ref name="Gorelli">{{cite journal
 | last = Gorelli
 | first = Federico A.
 | coauthors = Lorenzo Ulivi, Mario Santoro, and Roberto Bini
 | title = The ε Phase of Solid Oxygen: Evidence of an O<sub>4</sub> Molecule Lattice
 | journal = Physical Review Letters
 | volume = 83
 | issue = 20
 | pages = 4093–4096
 | doi = 10.1103/PhysRevLett.83.4093
 | url = http://link.aps.org/abstract/PRL/v83/p4093
 | format = abstract
 | bibcode = 1999PhRvL..83.4093G
 | date = November 1999
 | access-date = 2011-06-25
 | archive-date = 2008-11-22
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081122150619/http://link.aps.org/abstract/PRL/v83/p4093
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>然而2006年时，[[X射线晶体学|X射线晶体学]]表明这种被称作'''ε氧'''或'''红氧'''的稳定[[相_(物质)|相]]实际上是[[氧8|{{chem]]。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v443/n7108/abs/nature05174.html|title=Observation of an O8 molecular lattice in the  phase of solid oxygen|journal=Nature|volume=443|pages=201–204|date=2006-09-14|doi=10.1038/nature05174|accessdate=2008-01-10|author=Lars F. Lundegaard, Gunnar Weck, Malcolm I. McMahon, Serge Desgreniers and Paul Loubeyre|pmid=16971946|issue=7108|archive-date=2017-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627193444/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v443/n7108/abs/nature05174.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>  然而，氧4作为一种存在时间很短的化学物质已经能用[[质谱法|质谱法]]检测到。<ref name="Cacace">{{cite journal
 | last = Cacace
 | first = Fulvio
 | coauthors = Giulia de Petris, and Anna Troiani
 | title = Experimental Detection of Tetraoxygen
 | journal = Angewandte Chemie International Edition
 | volume = 40
 | issue = 21
 | pages = 4062–4065
 | doi = 10.1002/1521-3773(20011105)40:21<4062::AID-ANIE4062>3.0.CO;2-X
| pmid=12404493|date=October 2001}}</ref>

== 自由分子 ==

理论计算表明可能以[[亚稳态|亚稳态]]存在的O<sub>4</sub>分子有两种不同的结构：一种是变形的正方形（类似于[[环丁烷|环丁烷]]的稳定构象），<ref>{{cite journal
 | last = Hernández-Lamoneda
 | first = R.
 | coauthors = A. Ramírez-Solís
 | title = Reactivity and electronic states of O<sub>4</sub> along minimum energy paths
 | journal = Journal of Chemical Physics
 | volume = 113
 | issue = 10
 | pages = 4139–4145
 | doi = 10.1063/1.1288370
 |date=September 2000}}</ref>另一种的形状像风车，三个氧原子排列在中心氧原子周围，形成平面正三角形的构型（类似于[[三氟化硼|三氟化硼]]）。<ref>{{cite journal
 | last = Røeggen
 | first = I.
 | coauthors = E. Wisløff Nilssen
 | title = Prediction of a metastable D<sub>3h</sub> form of tetra oxygen
 | journal = Chemical Physics Letters
 | volume = 157
 | issue = 5
 | pages = 409–414
 | doi = 10.1016/0009-2614(89)87272-0
 |date=May 1989}}</ref><ref>Hotokka,M.; P.Pyykkö (May 1989). "Ab initio study of bonding trends in the series BO<sub>3<sup>3-</sup></sub>, CO<sub>3<sup>2-</sup></sub>, NO<sub>3<sup>-</sup></sub> and O<sub>4</sub>(D<sub>3h</sub>)". Chemical Physics Letters '''157'''(5):415-418.</ref>过去科学家指出风车形的O<sub>4</sub>分子可以看作一系列常见离子和分子的等电子体：[[硼酸根|BO<sub>3</sub><sup>3-</sup>]]、[[碳酸根|CO<sub>3</sub><sup>2-</sup>]]、[[硝酸根|NO<sub>3</sub><sup>-</sup>]]，<ref>Jubert,A.H.; E.L.Varetti (1986). "On the possible existence of the O<sub>4</sub> molecule with D<sub>3h</sub> symmetry". Anales de Química (Spain)'''82''':227-230.</ref>甚至包括类似的[[三氧化硫|SO<sub>3</sub>]]分子。这些看法是上述理论计算的基础。

